author: Seeking Alpha

description: This week we're joined by Will Thomson, Portfolio Manager and Founder at Massif Capital. We dive into everything! The recession (or not?,) Europe's woes, the strong US dollar and where it goes from here, the undersupply of precious metals, and so much more. Plus Kim covers why he's watching AMC earnings like a hawk next week for Catalyst Watch.
